  "blurb": "12 layers (SwiGLU 3.75x=1280, ~36.2M params) with NorMuon + Polar Express Muon(5-step) + FA3 Hopper. XSA(all 12) + CANON-AC(last 10) + GradQuant(8-seq probe: int8/int6/int5, 10/65/25%). Full GPTQ (Hessian-aware Cholesky error compensation, actorder, 256-seq calibration, 7+6 percentile search). NO global TTT (PR #596 style: all time to per-doc LoRA). Batched Per-document Q/K/V/Proj LoRA TTT (PR #611+: K 0.3x LR, Proj 0.2x LR, 96-192 docs parallel, rank-8 Q/K/V/Proj + rank-16 LM-head, 30 all-batched passes, per-batch LR cycling (5 candidates pass 0, 3 candidates passes 1-7), chunk diversity 256/512/1024/2048/4096, per-module LR scaling: Q 0.5x K 0.3x V 1.5x Proj 0.2x LM-head 2x bias 3x, baddbmm fused LoRA, batched bias tuning, score-every-epoch, skip-epoch0-scoring, front-loaded 3.0x/1.5x time allocation, no label smoothing, reduced training temps 3/25, batched early stopping, OOM protection, progressive PonderTTT 25/40/50%, ~580s budget). 25-temp diversity (T±0.52). Final sliding window (stride=48, 15s reserve). Soft-Round QAT (sigmoid soft-round, temp anneal 1→16). 5% pruning. Global eval timer + profiler. EMA 0.997 + exp-SWA(0.85). zstd-22.",
